gov.nih.nlm.nls.metamap.dfbuilder

Class ExtractMrstySemanticTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nih.nlm.nls.metamap.dfbuilder.ExtractMrstySemanticTypes

  • public class ExtractMrstySemanticTypes
extends Object
    Extract Mrsty Semantic Types Purpose: Extracts semantic type information from mrsty.eng.

    MRSTY column

    CUI
    Unique indentifier of concept
    TUI
    Unique indentifier of Semantic Type
    STN
    Semantic Type tree number.
    STY
    Semantic Type.
    ATUI
    Unique indentifier for attribute
    CVF
    Content View Flag
    Format of cui -> semantic type output file.
    CUI Concept Unique Identifier field 0
    ST Semantic Type field 1
